details.name: Wild Axes
details.description: Beastmaster sends his axes flying and calls them home again, slicing through enemy units and trees along their path.  Each axe can hit an enemy once, and amplifies subsequent damage from Beastmaster and his units. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.
details.upgrade_description: Causes Wild Axes to have no cooldown, and can be used again once they come back.
